5700.name: Seed: Alternative Great Cobol
5700.description: Plant this seed onto a monster in the Innadril area and it will bear the fruit of the Alternative Great Cobol. For best results, a level 41-51 character must plant it on a level 41-51 monster. Sowing

5701.name: Seed: Alternative Red Codran
5701.description: Plant this seed onto a monster in the Innadril area and it will bear the fruit of the Alternative Red Codran. For best results, a level 44-54 character must plant it on a level 44-54 monster. Sowing

5702.name: Seed: Alternative Sea Codran
5702.description: Plant this seed onto a monster in the Innadril area and it will bear the fruit of the Alternative Sea Codran. For best results, a level 44-54 character must plant it on a level 44-54 monster. Sowing

5703.name: Lucky Charm
5703.description: Bestows blessing on its owner such that when the owner dies during a boss/raid war, his/her abilities will not be diminished. This item can only be used on self by a character whose level is 19 or below. Raid Blessing

5705.name: Keshanberk*Damascus
5705.description: When enchanted, P. Atk. of a dualsword will increase more significantly than that of one-handed or fist weapon. When enchanted to 4 or more, Max HP will increase by 25% as well. Enhances damage to target during PvP.

5706.name: Damascus*Damascus
5706.description: When enchanted, P. Atk. of a dualsword will increase more significantly than that of one-handed or fist weapon. When enchanted to 4 or more, Accuracy will increase by 6. Enhances damage to target during PvP.

5707.name: Record of Seven Signs
5707.description: An item used for studying the current situation of the Seven Signs system.

5708.name: Lord of the Manor's Certificate of Approval
5708.description: When one possesses this item, although one does not belong to a castle owning clan, one can join the Lords of Dawn.
